{"tid":773221,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那繼假疫苗後 再爆有假生理食鹽水","createTime":"2018-08-09T10:48:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-09T21:23:15.000Z","uid":32511,"like":29,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"e93b894909a67334e8bed693e724cc345905886a","tid":773221,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T10:48:50.000Z","msg":"大陸繼日前的假疫苗風波後，近期又爆連生理食鹽水也有假貨流竄市面。浙江省浦江縣的<br />\n市場監督管理局發現，有間美容院的生理食鹽水竟然是「黑心貨」，追查後發現生理食鹽<br />\n水其實就只是水加上鹽，根本不是專業廠房所出產，目前已流出約8000件假生理食鹽水，<br />\n全大陸有24個省級行政區、4個直轄市中標。<br />\n <br />\n警方表示，生產的廠商在網路上開了4家店舖，販售包括生理食鹽水在內的假產品，當地<br />\n警方發現假藥目前已流入大陸24個省級行政區、4個直轄市，銷售總數近8000件。<br />\n <br />\n警方強調，藥品的標識全是英文，代表該產品未獲大陸官方認可，調查後還發現生理食鹽<br />\n水只是簡單的鹽、水混合，若是遭誤用於醫療用途，後果不堪設想。"},{"pid":"b9a60b53805b43eca0a5b7f8d84b32c2f0e2272a","tid":773221,"uid":170229,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T10:51:16.000Z","msg":"Normal saline (NSS, NS or N/S) is the commonly used phrase for a solution of 0.90% w/v of NaCl, 308 mOsm/L or 9.0 g per litre."},{"pid":"1dc7a806f9e721062ef5177b32fc77582999bed4","tid":773221,"uid":186177,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9a60b53805b43eca0a5b7f8d84b32c2f0e2272a","tid":773221,"uid":170229,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T10:51:16.000Z","msg":"Normal saline (NSS, NS or N/S) is the commonly used phrase for a solution of 0.90% w/v of NaCl, 308 mOsm/L or 9.0 g per litre."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T10:58:01.000Z","msg":"佢果隻有菌㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b2d37526dc09685d6939a3ee80ecabf7060bd4c","tid":773221,"uid":44454,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T11:02:51.000Z","msg":"香港大學專家：假生理鹽水不一定有害"},{"pid":"07f7739d7050d8f061b273ca8bf6b03ebe5d32b9","tid":773221,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T11:04:04.000Z","msg":"又掃貨？"},{"pid":"4097f938772725ca51c974d201d0b89548b065a5","tid":773221,"uid":12021,"like":